t are some options for beautiful gray hair with minimum care use a shampoo that is formulated to boost shine which gray hair can often lack shikai color reflect platinum shampoo is a shampoo that minimizes yellow a huge problem for gray hair this product gives me crazy shine like my head could standin for the sun on cloudy days make friends with your conditioner consider it your bestie youre going to want to keep your hair supermoisturized gray hair has less of a protective cuticle who knew so strands can get coarser and tend to break more easily its crucial to keep that hair hydrated for optimal shape giovanni chic brazilian keratin  argan oil ultrasleek conditioner is a conditioner that fights frizz which can be a common issue for gray hair this formula is like a gift straight from the goddess apply a deep conditioning treatment to pump up shine and repair hair cuticles about once a week — or whenever you damn well please its your hair for petes sake i like vitamin e because we tend to have an abundance of it in my house at all times but coconut olive and avocado oils are all groovy choices too slather your head with the oil of your choosing slap a scarf on that noggin and go to sleep wake up wash it out and get ready for the gushing youll receive from strangers on the street add vitamins b and b — and oh yeah why not add a high quality fish oil while your at it — to your daily supplement regime because they are good for healthy hair growth try to stick with lightweight styling products because gray hair can take on a greasy look really quickly also avoid products containing alcohol which can be super drying to already fragile hair i like alba botanica strong hold style gel because its fragrancefree and the older i get the more artificial scents really bother me my nostrils have been assaulted enough in my lifetime thank you very much stay out of direct sunlight because it can make hair dulllooking but if you’re the outdoor type which is a really great song by the way wear a hat or a dramatic head wrap imagine youre little edie in grey gardens if your end goal is to stop dyeing your hair but youre really unhappy about the contrast between gray roots and your colortreated areas professionals recommend getting lowlights to help ease the transition alternatively you can shave your head or you can just not freak out about it and just let your hair be a few color different colors for a while think of it as your own personal rainbow have you embraced gray hair what products have worked best for you share this please enable javascript to view the comments powered by disqus related stories what are your alltime favorite xovain articles its gonna get sappy up in here author marci december   open thread talk about beauty all day and all night long heres your place to come talk about hair makeup nails skincare whateverwhenever you feel like it author xojanestaff december   the only beauty advice i can give you for  dont change a thing but also change everything author sable december    makeup looks inspired by my favorite albums of  since im a visual person i hardly ever remember the album title but i just remember what the album art looks like author maura december   lotw a nod to my firstever look of the week its been such a big part of my journey here author tamaraanderson december   heres everything you wanted to know about makeup geeks new lipsticks or just look at the pretty pictures author allison december   pages         … next › last » see more   articles  dherbs  herbal supplements herbal remedies natural healing remedies full body detox storeherbal supplementscleansesmenwomenchildrensalesask the herbalistpreviously answeredresourcesarticlesaz health conditionsdetox troubleshootingfood combining chartfrequent product questionsdhtvrecipesblogabout usnewsinterviewscustomer servicelocal pickupsshipping  returns policysite troubleshootingdherbs rewards pointscontact us toll free   • international   articles articles  featured  he